.TH "dccp_wait_for_ccid" 9 "dccp_wait_for_ccid" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dccp_wait_for_ccid \- Await CCID send permission
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dccp_wait_for_ccid
.BI "(struct sock *sk "  ","
.BI "unsigned long delay "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sk" 12
socket to wait for
.IP "delay" 12
timeout in jiffies
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This is used by CCIDs which need to delay the send time in process context.
